1
00:01:29,480 --> 00:01:30,920
You already know

2
00:01:32,440 --> 00:01:34,370
about the test results, don't you?

3
00:01:34,479 --> 00:01:35,280
Shen Zhixia.

4
00:01:36,880 --> 00:01:38,940
Since your first day in the Lu family,

5
00:01:39,400 --> 00:01:41,860
how many things have you been hiding from me?

6
00:01:43,280 --> 00:01:44,759
Dad forced me to get a divorce,

7
00:01:44,759 --> 00:01:45,890
but I didn't give in.

8
00:01:47,120 --> 00:01:48,440
When Lu Jingxi bullied you,

9
00:01:48,440 --> 00:01:49,520
I protected you.

10
00:01:50,240 --> 00:01:51,840
What else do you want me to do?

11
00:01:53,880 --> 00:01:56,479
I... I know

12
00:01:57,680 --> 00:01:58,520
it's unfair to you.

13
00:01:58,520 --> 00:01:59,240
But

14
00:02:01,200 --> 00:02:03,360
I have decided to raise the child.

15
00:02:08,759 --> 00:02:09,960
Lu Jingheng.

16
00:02:10,240 --> 00:02:11,760
How I wish I could tell you

17
00:02:12,080 --> 00:02:13,720
that none of this is true.

18
00:02:14,120 --> 00:02:15,320
But I can't.

19
00:02:15,720 --> 00:02:16,760
Forgive me.

20
00:02:17,200 --> 00:02:19,360
I can't leave her child behind,

21
00:02:19,840 --> 00:02:22,760
even if the price is losing you.

22
00:02:31,800 --> 00:02:32,600
Let's

23
00:02:35,680 --> 00:02:36,680
get a divorce.

24
00:02:53,920 --> 00:02:54,680
Let's go.

25
00:03:03,560 --> 00:03:05,020
For everything recently,

26
00:03:07,480 --> 00:03:08,360
thank you.

27
00:03:54,440 --> 00:03:55,200
Don't worry.

28
00:03:55,200 --> 00:03:56,440
I know what I'm doing.

29
00:03:56,440 --> 00:03:57,640
I won't cause you trouble,

30
00:03:57,640 --> 00:03:59,280
let alone the Lu family.

31
00:03:59,440 --> 00:04:01,240
We're just a couple in name only.

32
00:04:01,240 --> 00:04:03,080
We'll go our separate ways eventually.

33
00:04:03,080 --> 00:04:05,080
Can't we just mind our own business?

34
00:04:07,520 --> 00:04:08,280
Shen Zhixia.

35
00:04:09,400 --> 00:04:11,360
How long are you going to play dumb?

36
00:04:13,280 --> 00:04:15,400
Watching me worry about you like this.

37
00:04:15,400 --> 00:04:16,480
Is it funny?

38
00:04:20,880 --> 00:04:21,680
Three days.

39
00:04:22,600 --> 00:04:23,520
Give me another three days.

40
00:04:23,520 --> 00:04:25,160
I will tell you everything that happened,

41
00:04:25,160 --> 00:04:28,090
exactly as it was, without leaving out a single word.

42
00:05:19,480 --> 00:05:20,720
Only for a better self.

43
00:05:20,720 --> 00:05:22,080
Every punch is for a better self.

44
00:05:22,080 --> 00:05:23,800
Look at our job ad.

45
00:05:24,440 --> 00:05:26,500
I don't mean to pour cold water on you.

46
00:05:26,760 --> 00:05:29,440
But being a boxing coach is no joke.

47
00:05:29,520 --> 00:05:30,920
Look at your small build.

48
00:05:31,040 --> 00:05:32,800
You don't look like a boxing coach at all.

49
00:05:32,800 --> 00:05:33,600
You

50
00:05:33,800 --> 00:05:35,120
should find a more suitable

51
00:05:35,120 --> 00:05:36,600
and comfortable job.

52
00:05:36,960 --> 00:05:37,760
Director.

53
00:05:37,880 --> 00:05:39,080
I've been practicing boxing since I was a child.

54
00:05:39,080 --> 00:05:40,240
I have more than ten years of experience.

55
00:05:40,240 --> 00:05:41,200
I can do this.

56
00:05:41,240 --> 00:05:42,040
You.

57
00:05:42,960 --> 00:05:43,760
Shen Zhixia.

58
00:05:45,400 --> 00:05:46,200
Mr. Wen.

59
00:05:50,080 --> 00:05:50,940
Wen Zhuocheng,

60
00:05:51,120 --> 00:05:52,520
Jingheng's good friend.

61
00:05:52,880 --> 00:05:53,680
Mr. Wen.

62
00:05:54,320 --> 00:05:55,440
You are friends.

63
00:05:55,680 --> 00:05:56,960
This is Mrs. Lu,

64
00:05:57,040 --> 00:05:58,280
Lu Jingheng's wife.

65
00:05:59,520 --> 00:06:00,480
Excuse me,

66
00:06:00,520 --> 00:06:01,360
Mrs. Lu.

67
00:06:01,440 --> 00:06:03,160
I failed to recognize you just now.

68
00:06:03,160 --> 00:06:04,480
Please don't take it to heart.

69
00:06:04,480 --> 00:06:07,360
Speaking of which, the boxing gym originally belonged to Mrs. Lu,

70
00:06:07,360 --> 00:06:08,880
and was later transferred to Mr. Lu.

71
00:06:08,880 --> 00:06:10,840
Mr. Lu transferred it to me to manage.

72
00:06:10,840 --> 00:06:12,160
What brings

73
00:06:12,160 --> 00:06:15,040
Mrs. Lu back here?

74
00:06:15,480 --> 00:06:16,280
No.

75
00:06:16,480 --> 00:06:18,200
Don't call me Mrs. Lu anymore.

76
00:06:18,240 --> 00:06:20,200
Lu Jingheng and I are discussing divorce.

77
00:06:20,200 --> 00:06:21,800
I'm here to look for a job today.

78
00:06:21,800 --> 00:06:23,440
Mr. Wen, if you trust me,

79
00:06:23,440 --> 00:06:24,480
you can give me a chance.

80
00:06:24,480 --> 00:06:25,760
I won't let you down.

81
00:06:27,800 --> 00:06:29,600
Miss Shen, you're being too modest.

82
00:06:29,600 --> 00:06:31,240
I've heard about your abilities for a long time.

83
00:06:31,240 --> 00:06:33,440
Your professionalism is beyond doubt.

84
00:06:33,920 --> 00:06:34,960
Take her to HR.

85
00:06:35,080 --> 00:06:36,159
As for the salary,

86
00:06:36,320 --> 00:06:39,159
we can negotiate based on a senior coach. Is that okay?

87
00:06:39,159 --> 00:06:40,800
Okay, Mrs. Lu.

88
00:06:41,120 --> 00:06:42,760
No, no, no, Coach Lu.

89
00:06:42,960 --> 00:06:44,960
Please come with me to the HR office.

90
00:06:44,960 --> 00:06:45,800
Wait a minute.

91
00:06:46,760 --> 00:06:47,760
Coach Shen.

92
00:06:50,080 --> 00:06:51,360
Coach Shen. Coach Shen.

93
00:06:51,360 --> 00:06:52,360
This way, please.

94
00:06:52,720 --> 00:06:53,480
Thank you.

95
00:06:53,480 --> 00:06:54,540
Welcome, welcome.

96
00:07:00,920 --> 00:07:01,720
Jingheng.

97
00:07:17,040 --> 00:07:17,880
Xingxing.

98
00:07:19,920 --> 00:07:22,600
You're Uncle Lu.

99
00:07:22,800 --> 00:07:24,040
It's me. Don't be afraid.

100
00:07:24,040 --> 00:07:24,960
Where is your mom?

101
00:07:24,960 --> 00:07:27,040
Mom and I live here.

102
00:07:27,120 --> 00:07:28,720
She is at work.

103
00:07:32,720 --> 00:07:34,200
You and your mom live here?

104
00:07:34,240 --> 00:07:37,880
Uncle Wen said he'd help Mom find a big house.

105
00:07:37,960 --> 00:07:39,440
Mom said there's no need.

106
00:07:39,480 --> 00:07:40,960
It's fine here.

107
00:07:40,960 --> 00:07:43,360
I can be with her every day.

108
00:07:46,960 --> 00:07:48,080
Why are you here?

109
00:07:53,520 --> 00:07:54,760
Zhuo Cheng told me.

110
00:07:59,360 --> 00:08:00,240
Use this card

111
00:08:00,880 --> 00:08:02,560
to find a better house.

112
00:08:03,160 --> 00:08:04,620
Don't let outsiders think

113
00:08:04,960 --> 00:08:06,920
the Lu family can't even afford this much.

114
00:08:06,920 --> 00:08:08,760
I am Coach Shen now.

115
00:08:08,920 --> 00:08:09,800
I have a job,

116
00:08:09,800 --> 00:08:11,860
and I can support myself and my child.

117
00:08:12,440 --> 00:08:13,500
I'm going to class.

118
00:08:13,840 --> 00:08:14,640
Xingxing,

119
00:08:14,880 --> 00:08:16,480
Mom will cook for you when she gets back.

120
00:08:16,480 --> 00:08:17,640
Okay, Mom.

121
00:08:23,360 --> 00:08:24,440
Hello, everyone.

122
00:08:25,000 --> 00:08:25,680
I thought

123
00:08:25,680 --> 00:08:27,880
Shen Zhixia on the registration was just a coincidence.

124
00:08:27,880 --> 00:08:28,600
Mrs. Lu.

125
00:08:28,600 --> 00:08:30,640
I didn't expect it to actually be Mrs. Lu.

126
00:08:30,640 --> 00:08:32,159
How did you end up

127
00:08:32,280 --> 00:08:33,360
as a boxing coach?

128
00:08:33,360 --> 00:08:35,960
If we had known Mrs. Lu made a living from this,

129
00:08:36,039 --> 00:08:38,370
we would have brought more friends along.

130
00:08:38,679 --> 00:08:39,480
Quiet.

131
00:08:39,720 --> 00:08:43,200
My first class is women's self-defense.

132
00:08:43,240 --> 00:08:45,720
It can save your life during a surprise attack.

133
00:08:45,720 --> 00:08:46,520
Coach Wang.

134
00:08:52,800 --> 00:08:54,200
A sneak attack from behind.

135
00:08:54,200 --> 00:08:56,640
Our first rule is to protect vital areas.

136
00:08:56,960 --> 00:08:59,800
Second is to use their momentum to strike back.

137
00:09:00,360 --> 00:09:03,280
Women are naturally not as physically strong as men.

138
00:09:03,280 --> 00:09:05,810
So we must attack the opponent's vital areas.

139
00:09:06,120 --> 00:09:06,920
The wrist.

140
00:09:07,280 --> 00:09:08,140
Under the ribs.

141
00:09:08,200 --> 00:09:09,520
This will give you time to escape.

142
00:09:09,520 --> 00:09:10,920
Did you see that clearly?

143
00:09:11,800 --> 00:09:12,600
Thank you.

144
00:09:14,360 --> 00:09:17,040
Women's self-defense is not a joke.

145
00:09:17,160 --> 00:09:19,960
It's meant to save your lives at critical moments.

146
00:09:20,320 --> 00:09:21,240
I know

147
00:09:21,240 --> 00:09:23,300
some people are just here for a laugh.

148
00:09:23,360 --> 00:09:24,200
But I also hope

149
00:09:24,200 --> 00:09:25,960
you can bring more people here.

150
00:09:26,080 --> 00:09:27,480
I'm not picky about my students.

151
00:09:27,480 --> 00:09:29,360
I just hope everyone can take it seriously

152
00:09:29,360 --> 00:09:30,820
and learn something here.

153
00:09:32,560 --> 00:09:33,690
These accessories,

154
00:09:33,800 --> 00:09:35,040
during training later,

155
00:09:35,040 --> 00:09:36,440
will not only hurt you,

156
00:09:36,720 --> 00:09:38,050
but also your partners.

157
00:09:38,320 --> 00:09:39,440
I'll give everyone a minute

158
00:09:39,440 --> 00:09:40,280
to adjust.

159
00:09:40,640 --> 00:09:41,600
Yes, Coach Shen.

160
00:09:43,240 --> 00:09:44,040
How is it?

161
00:09:44,400 --> 00:09:45,720
I didn't lie to you, right?

162
00:09:45,720 --> 00:09:47,800
Coach Shen is very professional.

163
00:09:50,160 --> 00:09:52,240
How did you two end up like this?

164
00:09:52,360 --> 00:09:54,320
Before, when your family forced you to get a divorce,

165
00:09:54,320 --> 00:09:55,520
you held your ground.

166
00:09:56,440 --> 00:09:58,500
Are you really getting a divorce now?

167
00:10:01,320 --> 00:10:03,680
I just gave you a casual call this morning.

168
00:10:03,800 --> 00:10:05,960
You dropped a meeting halfway through to rush over.

169
00:10:05,960 --> 00:10:08,760
Is this the attitude of someone getting a divorce?

170
00:10:10,040 --> 00:10:12,100
I have things to do. I'll leave first.

171
00:10:30,040 --> 00:10:31,600
The video conference with Ruiquan Group this afternoon

172
00:10:31,600 --> 00:10:32,560
has had its time confirmed.

173
00:10:32,560 --> 00:10:33,880
The materials have been sent to your email.

174
00:10:33,880 --> 00:10:34,920
The legal department

175
00:10:34,920 --> 00:10:35,720
wants to, before the meeting,

176
00:10:35,720 --> 00:10:38,080
reconfirm the capital injection terms with you.

177
00:10:38,080 --> 00:10:39,200
And then...

178
00:10:40,360 --> 00:10:41,160
Then what?

179
00:10:42,480 --> 00:10:43,800
There's one more thing.

180
00:10:43,800 --> 00:10:45,200
I don't know if I should say it.

181
00:10:45,200 --> 00:10:46,160
Just say it.

182
00:10:46,400 --> 00:10:47,660
Our lookout sent word.

183
00:10:48,000 --> 00:10:49,760
They say Master Wen has recently

184
00:10:49,760 --> 00:10:51,520
been pursuing the young madam.

185
00:11:06,840 --> 00:11:09,300
Coach Shen, you must be tired from training.

186
00:11:12,080 --> 00:11:12,940
These flowers,

187
00:11:13,440 --> 00:11:14,700
of course, are for you.

188
00:11:15,120 --> 00:11:16,360
You are so capable

189
00:11:17,000 --> 00:11:18,000
and independent.

190
00:11:18,640 --> 00:11:21,200
You are different from all the girls I've known.

191
00:11:21,200 --> 00:11:22,000
I...

192
00:11:22,280 --> 00:11:23,080
I mean,

193
00:11:24,400 --> 00:11:26,440
you and Lu Jingheng are over.

194
00:11:27,440 --> 00:11:29,240
Would you be willing to accept me

195
00:11:29,520 --> 00:11:30,840
and start a new...

196
00:11:30,960 --> 00:11:31,640
You can't do this.

197
00:11:31,640 --> 00:11:32,500
Wen Zhuocheng.

198
00:11:33,360 --> 00:11:34,290
What do you mean?

199
00:11:34,400 --> 00:11:35,330
What do you mean?

200
00:11:36,160 --> 00:11:36,960
Mr. Lu.

201
00:11:37,400 --> 00:11:38,240
We are already divorced.

202
00:11:38,240 --> 00:11:39,570
Stay out of my business.

203
00:11:39,960 --> 00:11:41,720
I have no right to interfere with your business.

204
00:11:41,720 --> 00:11:42,840
But you brought Little Star

205
00:11:42,840 --> 00:11:44,200
to live in a storage room.

206
00:11:44,200 --> 00:11:45,240
And you have

207
00:11:45,240 --> 00:11:47,040
an ill-intentioned suitor by your side.

208
00:11:47,040 --> 00:11:48,040
Do you think this is appropriate?

209
00:11:48,040 --> 00:11:49,160
Who is ill-intentioned?

210
00:11:49,160 --> 00:11:51,720
I have the final say on whether it's appropriate.

211
00:11:51,720 --> 00:11:52,800
Little Star is my child.

212
00:11:52,800 --> 00:11:54,330
I will take good care of him.

213
00:11:54,680 --> 00:11:55,360
You...

214
00:11:55,360 --> 00:11:57,290
Go vent your anger somewhere else.

215
00:11:57,760 --> 00:11:59,420
This is none of your business.

216
00:11:59,920 --> 00:12:02,040
Fine, I'm out.

217
00:12:02,960 --> 00:12:03,760
Goodbye.

218
00:12:06,880 --> 00:12:07,680
Mr. Lu.

219
00:12:07,920 --> 00:12:09,680
This is my workplace.

220
00:12:09,680 --> 00:12:12,120
Don't always bother me with personal matters.

221
00:12:12,120 --> 00:12:12,880
Go, go, go.

222
00:12:16,320 --> 00:12:18,850
Who says I'm here for personal matters today?

223
00:12:19,080 --> 00:12:20,680
I'm here today to sign up

224
00:12:22,160 --> 00:12:25,600
for private lessons.

225
00:12:27,160 --> 00:12:28,160
Private lessons?

226
00:12:29,640 --> 00:12:31,900
The most expensive ones for a whole year.

227
00:12:32,320 --> 00:12:33,250
Any objections?

228
00:12:34,800 --> 00:12:35,720
No objections.

229
00:12:36,000 --> 00:12:38,460
Pay enough, and the service will be perfect.

230
00:12:41,880 --> 00:12:42,680
Coach Shen.

231
00:12:42,960 --> 00:12:45,360
You can start scheduling my classes today.

232
00:12:47,400 --> 00:12:48,280
Today?

